{
  "stem": "19969.3",
  "chunk_idx": 1,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 19.9,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "We found ourselves faced with a masonry-- high masonry wall.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "Well, I couldn't-- it was hard to scramble over.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "And I, I left my radio and my radio operator and my jeep-- at that time, I was in a jeep.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "Or I had been.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "And so I left them outside the camp.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "And so I did not have my radio when I went in.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 34,
      "text": "What I had was my rifleman.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 35,
      "text": "There was always a rifleman with me.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 36,
      "text": "He was sort of my bodyguard.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 37,
      "text": "And I had an interpreter, a German interpreter.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 38,
      "text": "That is, he was an American soldier.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 39,
      "text": "But he was born in Germany.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 40,
      "text": "He was a young American soldier.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 41,
      "text": "He Migrated to Germany.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 42,
      "text": "His father was a professor at some college in Germany.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 43,
      "text": "And he did not like Hitler.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 44,
      "text": "So he got out while he could.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 45,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] And I think the soldier was, like, 10 years old when he came to the States because he spoke obviously fluent German.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Hmm?",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "He was not Jewish.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "His name was Karl Mann.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And he was about 19 years old at the time, just out of high school.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And he was with me all the time-- and the rifleman.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "The three of us were always right together because I had-- an interpreter, you know, was invaluable to me.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And the rifleman I used also to carry messages or to give orders back and forth.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And we climbed over the wall, following the right patroon, which would fan out on a long skirmish line.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And each man went over.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "Now, we did not receive any fire from the Germans, which-- [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] I, I really wasn't anticipating much of a battle there.",
      "word_count": 25
    }
  ],
